ing replicated properties and RPCs."},{"heading":"12. VR & AR","content":"Develop immersive experiences with Motion Controllers and AR Core/Kit."},{"heading":"13. Asset Management & Marketplace","content":"Import/export assets and use Marketplace and Quixel library."},{"heading":"14. Performance Optimization","content":"Profile with GPU profiler, optimize draw calls, LODs, and memory."},{"heading":"15. Packaging & Deployment","content":"Package for PC, consoles, mobile, VR, and configure launch settings."},{"heading":"16. Source Control & CI","content":"Use Git LFS, Perforce, and integrate build pipelines."},{"heading":"17. C++ Plugins & Editor Tools","content":"Extend the editor or build plugins in C++."},{"heading":"18. QA Testing","content":"Write functional tests, automation scripts, and use Test framework."},{"heading":"19. Documentation & Community","content":"Use Unreal Online Learning, forums, and Youtube tutorials."},{"heading":"20. Best Practices","content":"- Use Visual Logger\n- Modularize Blueprints\n- Package asset dependencies\n- Leverage data-only Blueprints"}],"related":["zustand-roadmap","playwright-roadmap","recoil-roadmap","prometheus-roadmap","django-roadmap"]},{"slug":"blender-roadmap","title":"Blender Roadmap: A Complete Guide [2025 Updated]","description":"Master Blender in 2025 with this roadmap covering core modeling, shading, animation, simulation, scripting, and add-on development.","sections":[{"heading":"What is Blender?","content":"Blender is a free, open-source 3D creation suite supporting modeling, rigging, animation, simulation, rendering, compositing, and video editing."},{"heading":"Why Blender?","content":"A complete, versatile toolset with cycles/Eevee rendering, Python scripting, asset management, and active community."},{"heading":"1. Install & Setup","content":"Download from blender.org, enable add-ons and configure input preferences."},{"heading":"2. Viewport & UI","content":"Learn using 3D viewport, panels, workspaces, Outl