ity"},{"heading":"16. Ecosystem Maturity","content":"Exceeded 70 M monthly downloads, overtaking OpenAI SDK, built environment geared toward large‑scale deployments"},{"heading":"17. Future Focus","content":"Better debugging tools, expanded LCEL support, deeper security, integrations, and enterprise readiness"},{"heading":"18. Best Practices","content":"Use templates/defaults, monitor via LangSmith, secure pipelines, version agent definitions, test with open evals"}],"related":["graphql-roadmap","sql-roadmap","nodejs-roadmap","hasura-roadmap","laravel-roadmap"]},{"slug":"huggingface-roadmap","title":"Hugging Face Roadmap: A Complete Guide [2025 Updated]","description":"Master Hugging Face in 2025 with this roadmap covering transformers, multimodal, federated learning, robotics, edge AI, and open-source innovation.","sections":[{"heading":"What is Hugging Face?","content":"A leading open‑source AI platform offering Transformers library, model hosting, datasets, inference APIs, courses, and robotics integrations"},{"heading":"Why Hugging Face?","content":"Empowers researchers & devs with open models, multimodal pipelines, federated fine‑tuning, real‑time edge inference, and robotics democratization"},{"heading":"1. Transformers Growth","content":"Evolving from NLP to multimodal models (text+image+audio) and supporting federated learning, explainable AI, on‑device pipelines"},{"heading":"2. Sparse & Dense Embeddings","content":"Sentence‑Transformers v5.0 adds high‑dim sparse encoders for hybrid search use‑cases"},{"heading":"3. Federated & Edge Learning","content":"Native support for federated fine‑tuning with PySyft and TorchScript/JIT for edge deployments"},{"heading":"4. Explainable AI (XAI)","content":"Integration with Captum, SHAP, LIME for model interpretability"},{"heading":"5. Distributed Training & Scaling","content":"Support for DeepSpeed, Horovod, Ray, ZeRO, TPU/Inferentia optimizations"},{"heading":"6. Reinforcement Learning Integration","content":"RLHF & S